{
  "stem": "8916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, she-- in Narewka, she was surrounded by her family and friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when she moved to Krakow, she's just had to start all over again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's like practically moving to a new country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not-- not much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was-- she was a strong woman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she was efficient and hard-working, so that when she had-- when something had to be done, she just went to it and did it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She may-- may have fallen apart later on, you know, but when it was-- the thing had to be done, she-- she just went ahead and did it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we continued until the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It broke-- we-- we had only been there one year and the war broke out in 1939 and Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When that started, of course, it was, as we know now, was the beginning of a very dark, dark period in-- in history of Europe and in-- in our personal history.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as soon as the Germans came in, their campaign against Jews was immediately apparent, although in the beginning, it looked like just occasional drunken soldiers bored with being-- you know, just bored with army life and just having fun with Jews, beating them up or making them do things that are--",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And dragging them down the street making and making them clean the streets or kneel or whatever just to humiliate them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But as time went on, it was not long before we knew that there was a definite campaign that they're-- they were waging against the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the laws were being passed almost daily.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, immediately, as soon as the Germans came in, we were immediately thrown out of school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish children couldn't go to public school.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
